4577.title: Dora the Explorer
4577.description: Dora remembers the first time she met her friend Backpack. Backpack is helping Dora carry her books back to the Library. Can they reach the Library before it closes?

4578.title: Dora the Explorer
4578.description: Dora and Boots offer to help Mama Bugga Bugga bring a giant cookie home to feed her babies.

11002.title: Dora the Explorer
11002.description: Dora and Boots go on an underwater adventure that takes them all the way to the bottom of the ocean.

11003.title: Dora the Explorer
11003.description: Dora and Boots are getting ready to make a wish on the first star in the sky when the star falls! It's up to Dora and Boots to bring Little Star back home to the Moon.

17080.title: Dora the Explorer
17080.description: Dora and Boots must go into a storybook to rescue a prince from a wicked witch.

17081.title: Dora the Explorer
17081.description: In this version of the famous Puerto Rican legend, Dora and Boots find a sad, homesick little coqui who's lost his voice. Dora and Boots offer to take the frog home to his island.

22874.title: Dora the Explorer
22874.description: Abuela tells Dora and Boots about a magical Chocolate Tree that lived near her house when she was a little girl. Dora and Boots set off into the forest to find it!

22875.title: Dora the Explorer
22875.description: El Mago, a mean magician, casts a spell on King Popo and Queen Maria, turning them into mountains so they can never be together. Can our heroes break the spell?

29181.title: Dora the Explorer
29181.description: When young Pablo loses his magic flute, a terrible drought hits his family's farm. Dora and Boots find Pablo's flute, and hurry off to return it to Pablo on his Mountain.

29182.title: Dora the Explorer
29182.description: Dora and Boots keep running into friends in need of help. Turns out the other animals are all headed to a big party at the Treehouse. They beg Dora and Boots to come too!

35852.title: Dora the Explorer
35852.description: Boots is thrilled to hear about the riddle contest today at the Tall Mountain. Who can solve the silliest riddle?

35853.title: Dora the Explorer
35853.description: Uh oh! A Big Storm Cloud is coming. Dora and Boots have to warn all their friends in the forest to get home fast so the Big Storm Cloud doesn't rain on them and get them wet.

42247.title: Dora the Explorer
42247.description: Boots can't wait for a super duper toy fire truck that's coming in the mail. But when the package arrives, the box is empty! Seems the toy fell out and is now sitting far away on top of Snowy Mountain.

42248.title: Dora the Explorer
42248.description: The stick, the stick, the Magic Stick! Dora and Boots find a magic stick and according to the wise old Tree Frog, it's up to our two young heroes to go to the top of the Highest Hill to make the stick do its magic trick.

49152.title: Dora the Explorer
49152.description: ¡Falta algo! Something's missing! Dora and Boots meet a wizard, El Encantador, who's missing his magic wand! Dora and Boots set off to find El Encantador's wand so he can do his magic.

49153.title: Dora the Explorer
49153.description: Squeaky, squeaky! What's that sound? It's Squeaky, Boots' adorably squeezable new bath toy. But when Boots loses Squeaky, we all have to head to the Gooey Geyser to get him back.

55678.title: Dora the Explorer
55678.description: Meet Rojo, the newest, shiniest red fire truck. Rojo invites our heroes along as he goes on his very first rescue mission - to help a kitten who's stuck in a tree.

55679.title: Dora the Explorer
55679.description: Who do we ask for help when we don't know which way to go? The Map! But today the Map gets mistaken for a stick by a goofy bird. The bird flies Map all the way to his nest on top of Tallest Mountain.

62233.title: Dora the Explorer
62233.description: It's Mother's Day, and Dora wants to help Papi bake Mamá a special cake. But three key ingredients are missing: bananas, nuts and chocolate.

62234.title: Dora the Explorer
62234.description: Go-go-go-golden Explorers! Dora and her friends have formed a soccer team and are playing the big Dinosaurs. Can Dora kick the ball into the net and score a goal?

68207.title: Dora the Explorer
68207.description: Achoo, achoo! What's that sound? Benny the Bull has the sneezes. It's Doctor Dora to the rescue as she sets off to Benny's Barn for a house call.

68208.title: Dora the Explorer
68208.description: Yee haw! Cowgirl Dora and Cowboy Boots are riding through the Wild West on Pinto the Pony Express. They have to deliver a special package of cowboy cookies to Benny the Bull, but they'll have to be on the lookout for Swiper.

74602.title: Dora the Explorer
74602.description: Dora and Boots meet León, a friendly lion who wants to join the circus. They pedal on a unicycle, tightrope walk and skate their way to the Big Top, so León can become a circus lion and do all his tricks.

74603.title: Dora the Explorer
74603.description: Step right up and join the fiesta! Dora and Boots are trying to win the grand prize - the Big Piñata! They need to collect 10 yellow tickets by playing carnival games and rides.

81248.title: Dora the Explorer
81248.description: We all have something that makes us happy, even the Grumpy Old Troll! Dora and Boots set off on a quest to find all the things that make the Grumpy Old Troll happy, so he can do his happy dance.

81249.title: Dora the Explorer
81249.description: Nothing can stop Dora and Boots, they will not fail! Their job is to deliver the mail! Dora and Boots are mail carriers and they need to deliver all the letters, even one to Swiper the Fox!

88091.title: Dora the Explorer
88091.description: Map finds a red cape and becomes super hero for the day. He can jump, he can fly, he can blow clouds away with a single, super breath! He's Super Map! When Dora's mommy calls her home, Dora and Boots need to get home fast.

88092.title: Dora the Explorer
88092.description: Dora has tried and tried, but she's never been able to climb all the way across the monkey bars. Dora and Boots set off for Play Park so Dora can give it another try.

94701.title: Dora the Explorer
94701.description: C'mon and join the musical parade! Dora and Boots are leading a parade over the Piano Bridge and through the Swinging Gate to free the instruments that were locked up by the evil Señor Shhh!

94702.title: Dora the Explorer
94702.description: Dora and her friends are super good at hiding, especially Señor Tucán when he hides in the Rain Forest. If we can find all 8 friends, Señor Tucán promises to introduce us to his new baby toucans.
